#

Sweet Pickles

10 min
$5
40 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

SnackCondimentEasy

Description

Sweet and tangy with a delightful crunch, these pickles are a perfect snack or condiment!

Ingredients

  • cucumber: 4-5 medium
  • sugar: 1 cup
  • white vinegar: 1 cup
  • water: 1 cup
  • salt: 2 tablespoons
  • onion: 1, sliced
  • mustard seeds: 1 tablespoon
  • celery seeds: 1 teaspoon
  • turmeric: 1 teaspoon
  • cinnamon stick: 1, optional
